  "title": "Channel Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p>We're looking for a Channel Sales Manager to drive growth through our partner network, selling physical security tech solutions (CCTV, access control, etc.)<br /><br /> Responsibilities</p><p>- Develop and execute channel sales strategies with partners (resellers, integrators, etc.)</p><p>- Build and manage partner relationships to drive security tech sales</p><p>- Identify and pursue new business opportunities through channel partners</p><p>- Provide sales support, training, and technical enablement to partners</p><p>- Collaborate with product and marketing teams to align channel efforts</p><p></p><p>- 2 years of experience in channel sales, preferably in security tech</p><p>- Strong communication and relationship-building skills</p><p>- Experience with partner management and sales enablement</p><p></p><p>Skills</p><p>- Channel sales strategy</p><p>- Partner relationship management</p><p>- Sales enablement</p><p>- Security tech knowledge</p><p>- Business development</p>",
